Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於能遇見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不幸丟失的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於能遇見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直缺失的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而將其毀掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你是不可饒恕的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:37.61,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:44.81,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:02:00.46,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:10.93,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:23.01,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:33.60,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:39.76,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:45.61,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:49.98,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:53.32,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.33,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:37.61,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:44.81,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們在倒錯的精神世界中相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:02:00.46,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我們眼裡的世界總是相互顛倒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:10.93,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,這幾乎要被認定為是無可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:23.01,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,傷口淌淚的眼眸 在內心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:33.60,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的兩人來不及結合便聽到離別的倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:39.76,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:45.61,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們像漸趨衰老的動物一樣相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:49.98,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:53.32,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,在倒錯的精神世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.33,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我想細細體會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}亞當的斷片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲那傢伙 竟敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希爾菲 我最可惡的臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯獨不能失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕這個世界變成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.44,0:03:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我叫做死神?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不完整的機械天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爲什麽能聽到他的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為原本我就是你 你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此我無法原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其無法原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.23,0:04:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你殺害了我們的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親? 你說的是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是Altair的最高領導者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出雲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你 一切都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膽小鬼阿馬塔給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然一個人就能合體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:05:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能辦到 我沒理由辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 我辦到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被一分為二的靈魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邂逅了機械天使的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:06:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻正是紅色的夢境與藍色的現實相会之际
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克雷雅理事长 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红色的行星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Altair
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到GEPART的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎正在与Abductor战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受我吧 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空间填補
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪 再说服下去也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续使用能力的话 你的身体會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么放弃的話 那Mix怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会放弃的 Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到用這雙手緊抱你为止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 为什么要为了我做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想填滿你的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌洞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去你會被Mix捏碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在以我填滿你心中裂开的大洞之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心中的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于能抱到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶的缺失部分正逐漸被填补
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所失去的…身為女人的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 一直出現在我記憶裏的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你恢复记忆了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪 我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经…不是女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使這樣也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男是女這無關緊要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢的就是Mix這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以跟你合体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 合体是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們明白现在是什么状况吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我堅守至今的純潔靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經我千锤百炼的节操
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今正是讓其爆发之時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夙愿合体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:10:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂 無論是爸爸還是媽媽都伴隨在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在Altair這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我不同 你身處在擁有一切的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不記得有被父母養育過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我養大的是未影 那個惡魔般的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他一起的生活是異常的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未影身邊 我感到比獨處時更加孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也無法信任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但第一次聞到臭女人…希爾菲的味道時我感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上只有這個女人能夠接受我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我命中註定的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要殺了希爾菲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秉承愛的名義 跟她互相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕要為此犧牲那對我只生不養的所謂親生父母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我軟弱的心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是軟弱的 你的愛也是軟弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.30,0:12:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一萬兩千年前我們才會和希爾菲天涯相隔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在一萬兩千年前后的現世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就眼看著母親離去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次又要把希爾菲給…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Altair進一步接近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且在不斷加速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像和互相碰撞的阿馬塔他們取得共鳴一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理事長?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是撰寫在創聖之書裏的新篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一分為二的靈魂在彼此呼喚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩顆星球亦隨之相互牽引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終交相碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陳舊的事物將會消失殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嶄新的世界將會應運而生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個未影將成為神的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所期待的未來也是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你一直在守望著這顆星球一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直在注視著你所選擇的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我一直注視著于任何時候都巋然不動的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了嶄新的世界 當今的生命將全部成為犧牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個學園的一眾學生也不會例外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為那是創聖之書所追求的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就一動不動地迎接大家的死亡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的覺得這樣就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不動·ZEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我初次邂逅御子乃的時候也覺得那是命運使然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是能接受我、和我感受到同樣痛苦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我對她的印象並不止這些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃她很怯弱 容易生氣 又愛莫名其妙地吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許你誇獎臭女人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但御子乃她又總是努力不懈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠體諒別人的痛苦 能夠讓大家團結一心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是希爾菲 而是現在的御子乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一派胡言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最喜歡的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要一手掌握命運
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要連命運也一併超越 擁抱現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃（希爾菲）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔和那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們不能夠戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔 神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能戰鬥?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否定戰鬥就相當於否定這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是和他們而是要和我合體喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃·鈴白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.41,0:16:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是 愛的失敗者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:17:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩萬四千年前 跟我締有婚約的男人背叛了我的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懷揣著這份仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿波羅尼亞斯的轉世阿波羅戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那時我還未能完全割捨那揮之不去的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波羅為了拯救世界而希望與我合為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我對此予以了接受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想到要和深愛的人合為一體 我就感到欣喜若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我在靈魂相融的那一瞬間察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波羅並不是阿波羅尼亞斯的轉世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的阿波羅尼亞斯是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波羅尼亞斯一而再地踐踏了我的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要將兩顆星球合而為一 並成為新世界的神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.74,0:18:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛的失敗者將毀滅所有的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我所追求的新神話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 我們合為一體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺死多少次也不足以解恨的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我身邊奪走阿波羅尼亞斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恨的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是復仇的婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是希爾菲的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃…御子乃在那機體裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要更多的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Iron C 將母星的力量賜予我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:20:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未影 是打算吸光星球的力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔 你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚葉 還有諸井
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你代替我合體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有你的Element能力 就無法和那些傢伙對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿馬塔同學 我們合體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決戰合體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GO Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion EVOL
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把御子乃還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Iron C 製裁他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,區區翼犬休想能反抗神的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後神樂…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神樂 你是不能反抗我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.75,0:21:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹂躪合體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.05,0:21:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GO Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 多麼美麗 又多麼空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.81,0:22:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色的…Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:57.93,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君へ続く坂道に 白い花が咲いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:23:05.74,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}夢から覚めたあとも 悲しい空見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:15.72,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}この気持ち葉っぱの裏に住んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:25.22,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}朝露が落ちる音に 耳をすませてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:33.08,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神様 あなたが造った世界は 完璧じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:40.67,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}ここでは毎日恋がポロポロ 死んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:44.86,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}はじめて好きになったの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:48.02,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたは知らないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:52.55,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}地球の裏側でいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:55.76,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:24:00.09,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}私を忘れてもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:06.60,nedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:57.93,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}延伸到你身旁的坡道 點綴著雪白的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:23:05.74,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}從睡夢中驚醒之後 遠望著憂傷的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:15.72,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}這份青澀的感覺 依存在綠葉錯綜的紋路之間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:25.22,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}側耳聆聽 晨露緩緩落下的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:33.08,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神明您所創造的這個世界並不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:40.67,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}因為這裡每天都有戀情一段接一段地告終
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.87,0:23:44.86,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我是初嘗戀愛的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:48.02,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}這個你應該不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:52.55,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即便永不見天日也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.73,0:23:55.76,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.95,0:24:00.09,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}就算你把我忘卻也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:06.60,jedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身邊
